.el .ds Aq '
.TH manta-config-unset 1  "unset " 
.SH NAME
manta\-config\-unset \- Clear a configuration value
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmanta config unset\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Clear a configuration value
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
manta\-config\-unset\-hsm(1)
Clear the active node group
.TP
manta\-config\-unset\-parent\-hsm(1)
Clear the parent node group
.TP
manta\-config\-unset\-auth(1)
Clear the cached authentication token
